**Information You Voluntarily Provide to Us:** The personal information we collect on or through our Services may include: 
     * **Account Registration:** information relating to the creation of an account on one of our Sites, such as first and last name, email address, postal address, telephone number, and/or a unique individual password;
     * **Contact Forms:** information added to form fields on our Services, including name, email address, and the contents of any accompanying message, such as to contact DomainsBot, set up a demonstration, request information or technical support, or download a white paper;
     * **Purchasing Services:** business contact information that is required to register for different DomainsBot subscription plans, including organization name and address, and business contact’s name, username, password, email, and country;
     * **Payment Information:** payment card, transaction or financial account information, if you make a purchase online or sign up via our order forms;
     * **“My DomainsBot” Content:** if you submit information to the DomainsBot “My DomainsBot” service, we will associate with your account your domain name information, including expiration date, DNS information, and registrar information.
